if you're wondering whether this might be for you...
Maybe you're a seeker, an endless explorer. You’re on the path, the ever-evolving journey of discovering & revealing who you are. You’re a gorgeous work in progress who’s okay with things sometimes being messy because that’s how we learn and how we grow.
--------- Maybe you’ve got a creative project in you that’s been stewing for a while, years even, and you could use some creative cross-training to exercise those muscles because you've been experiencing a creative or writer’s block so that you can find renewed inspiration and a way thru to take on that challenge and bring forth that business, book, or creative project that wants to come alive.
---------------
Maybe you need to reinvigorate your creativity or get to a new level in your creative expression or connect your creativity to your legacy and really do something impactful in the world.
-----------
Maybe you’re in transition from one part of your life to the next and you want to transition deliberately so that you can make bold decisions confidently, deeply trusting your intuition and knowing for the right next path.
----------
Maybe you just need some creative time for yourself to slow down and listen to what wants to come forward....a book, a new program or project, a new direction for your career.
---------
Maybe it’s been awhile since you’ve trusted your body and what it’s telling you. ---------
Maybe you’re looking for a better way of accessing that inner wisdom you know is inside of you.
-----------
Maybe you need time in a circle of women who are also seeing their truth to feel held, witnessed and loved.
